    "body": "Minimal repro here: https://github.com/gakonst/truffle-bug-repro.\r\n\r\nThe problem is that when using the `chainId: 1337`(e.g. with `geth --dev`), I get: `Error: Chain with ID 1337 not supported`, which [comes from ethereumjs-vm/common](https://github.com/ethereumjs/ethereumjs-monorepo/blob/cc9872972a657583eb1e3ef8d04b9f5b72562466/packages/common/src/index.ts#L103-L108)\r\n\r\nThe `chainId` seems to get set [here](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/2bbd6722e1807c42cb665c68d401cd857e86f628/packages/hdwallet-provider/src/index.ts#L158-L160).",
